在[[生态学|生态学]]中，'''占域'''是指一个区域被目标[[物种|物种]]占据的[[概率|概率]]。占域研究可以了解某个物种占据研究区域的比例、空间分布, 以及环境因素的影响<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wenhong |first1=Xiao |last2=Zufei |first2=Shu |last3=Lijun |first3=Chen |last4=Wutao |first4=Yao |last5=Yong |first5=Ma |last6=Yingming |first6=Zhang |last7=Zhishu |first7=Xiao |title=Using occupancy models in wildlife camera-trapping monitoring and the study case |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019 |volume=27 |issue=3 |pages=249–256 |doi=10.17520/biods.2018195}}</ref>。典型的占域研究包括确定整体样本、选择样本单元、基于样本单元开展调查并作出结论<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mackenzie |first1=Darryl I. |last2=Royle |first2=J. Andrew |title=Designing occupancy studies: general advice and allocating survey effort: Designing occupancy studies |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-ecology_2005-12_42_6/page/1105 |journal=Journal of Applied Ecology |date=2005-12 |volume=42 |issue=6 |pages=1105–1114 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2664.2005.01098.x}}</ref>。

